        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Como resultado <strong>vamos a</strong> <strong>conseguir una imagen gris</strong> con algunas texturas, si está de otro color entonces no lo estás haciendo bien (a mí me ha pasado). Verifica que los parámetros que ingresaste son los correctos.&nbsp;</p><p class="">Ahora vamos al panel de <strong>capas</strong> y en<strong> tipo de fusión</strong>, seleccionamos<strong> luz lineal</strong>.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eba5a754-4696-419f-b07d-6c3c3997a2dc/luz-lineal.jpg" data-image-dimensions="600x347" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eba5a754-4696-419f-b07d-6c3c3997a2dc/luz-lineal.jpg?format=1000w" width="600" height="347" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eba5a754-4696-419f-b07d-6c3c3997a2dc/luz-lineal.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eba5a754-4696-419f-b07d-6c3c3997a2dc/luz-lineal.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eba5a754-4696-419f-b07d-6c3c3997a2dc/luz-lineal.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eba5a754-4696-419f-b07d-6c3c3997a2dc/luz-lineal.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eba5a754-4696-419f-b07d-6c3c3997a2dc/luz-lineal.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eba5a754-4696-419f-b07d-6c3c3997a2dc/luz-lineal.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eba5a754-4696-419f-b07d-6c3c3997a2dc/luz-lineal.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Una vez hecho todo esto, podemos usar herramientas como el tampón clonar o el pincel corrector puntual para editar sobre la capa de color o textura para eliminar imperfecciones, hasta conseguir el resultado deseado.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/9e8f204f-a388-4772-9442-8a77d6649e85/foto-antes-y-despues.jpg" data-image-dimensions="600x442" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/9e8f204f-a388-4772-9442-8a77d6649e85/foto-antes-y-despues.jpg?format=1000w" width="600" height="442" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/9e8f204f-a388-4772-9442-8a77d6649e85/foto-antes-y-despues.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/9e8f204f-a388-4772-9442-8a77d6649e85/foto-antes-y-despues.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/9e8f204f-a388-4772-9442-8a77d6649e85/foto-antes-y-despues.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/9e8f204f-a388-4772-9442-8a77d6649e85/foto-antes-y-despues.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/9e8f204f-a388-4772-9442-8a77d6649e85/foto-antes-y-despues.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/9e8f204f-a388-4772-9442-8a77d6649e85/foto-antes-y-despues.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/9e8f204f-a388-4772-9442-8a77d6649e85/foto-antes-y-despues.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Hay detalles que se eliminan en la capa color y otros, que solo se pueden eliminar en la de textura, así que ojito con ello.</p><h2>Suavizar la piel con Photoshop</h2><p class="">Para dar un efecto de suavidad a la piel en Photoshop utilizaremos la técnica conocida como paso alto invertido.</p><p class="">La dejo para el final porque primero debemos eliminar las imperfecciones, ya sea con alguna de las técnicas que te mostré o cualquier otra.</p><p class="">Para aplicarla debemos seguir el siguiente paso a paso:</p><p class=""><strong>Duplicamos la capa</strong> sobre la cual estamos trabajando.</p><p class="">Con la capa superior seleccionada, nos vamos al menú y seleccionamos <strong>filtro</strong> &gt; <strong>otro</strong> &gt; <strong>Paso alto</strong>.</p><p class="">En esta ventana debemos seleccionar un número que sea divisible entre 3, claro, dependiendo del tamaño de la imagen, bien podría ser 12, 21 o 24, mayor o menor a estos valores.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3907d5bc-7ca9-4dd5-9047-b0c64fdba660/paso-alto.jpg" data-image-dimensions="448x400" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3907d5bc-7ca9-4dd5-9047-b0c64fdba660/paso-alto.jpg?format=1000w" width="448" height="400" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3907d5bc-7ca9-4dd5-9047-b0c64fdba660/paso-alto.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3907d5bc-7ca9-4dd5-9047-b0c64fdba660/paso-alto.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3907d5bc-7ca9-4dd5-9047-b0c64fdba660/paso-alto.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3907d5bc-7ca9-4dd5-9047-b0c64fdba660/paso-alto.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3907d5bc-7ca9-4dd5-9047-b0c64fdba660/paso-alto.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3907d5bc-7ca9-4dd5-9047-b0c64fdba660/paso-alto.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3907d5bc-7ca9-4dd5-9047-b0c64fdba660/paso-alto.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Ahora vamos a <strong>filtro</strong> &gt; <strong>Desenfocar</strong> &gt; <strong>desenfoque Gaussiano</strong>.</p><p class="">Aquí debemos seleccionar un valor que al multiplicarlo por 3, de como resultado el valor que elegimos en el paso alto. Si elegimos 12 en el paso alto, entonces debemos establecer 4.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/785eea7f-3bdb-4b0d-b8bd-c57d34257f42/desenfoque-gau.jpg" data-image-dimensions="468x374" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/785eea7f-3bdb-4b0d-b8bd-c57d34257f42/desenfoque-gau.jpg?format=1000w" width="468" height="374" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/785eea7f-3bdb-4b0d-b8bd-c57d34257f42/desenfoque-gau.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/785eea7f-3bdb-4b0d-b8bd-c57d34257f42/desenfoque-gau.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/785eea7f-3bdb-4b0d-b8bd-c57d34257f42/desenfoque-gau.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/785eea7f-3bdb-4b0d-b8bd-c57d34257f42/desenfoque-gau.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/785eea7f-3bdb-4b0d-b8bd-c57d34257f42/desenfoque-gau.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/785eea7f-3bdb-4b0d-b8bd-c57d34257f42/desenfoque-gau.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/785eea7f-3bdb-4b0d-b8bd-c57d34257f42/desenfoque-gau.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class=""><strong>Invertimos la capa</strong> utilizando el Ctrl + i o en Mac Cmd + i.</p><p class="">Luego cambiamos el modo de fusión a <strong>luz intensa.</strong></p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/03d8b0a2-e1de-416b-9f45-716de4b66ef7/luz-intensa.jpg" data-image-dimensions="600x353" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/03d8b0a2-e1de-416b-9f45-716de4b66ef7/luz-intensa.jpg?format=1000w" width="600" height="353" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/03d8b0a2-e1de-416b-9f45-716de4b66ef7/luz-intensa.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/03d8b0a2-e1de-416b-9f45-716de4b66ef7/luz-intensa.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/03d8b0a2-e1de-416b-9f45-716de4b66ef7/luz-intensa.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/03d8b0a2-e1de-416b-9f45-716de4b66ef7/luz-intensa.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/03d8b0a2-e1de-416b-9f45-716de4b66ef7/luz-intensa.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/03d8b0a2-e1de-416b-9f45-716de4b66ef7/luz-intensa.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/03d8b0a2-e1de-416b-9f45-716de4b66ef7/luz-intensa.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Por último,<strong> creamos una máscara de capa pulsando alt</strong> y pintamos con el pincel blanco sobre las zonas que queramos suavizar.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
