        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h3>Agrupar capas</h3><p class="">Esta opción permite seleccionar varias capas y crear una carpeta en la cual estarán contenidas todas las capas seleccionadas.</p><p class="">Es muy útil por si no quieres ocupar todo el panel con capas del mismo&nbsp;</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3127ab14-d3ca-48de-8a44-20db8571bf84/agrupar-capas.jpg" data-image-dimensions="347x131" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3127ab14-d3ca-48de-8a44-20db8571bf84/agrupar-capas.jpg?format=1000w" width="347" height="131" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3127ab14-d3ca-48de-8a44-20db8571bf84/agrupar-capas.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3127ab14-d3ca-48de-8a44-20db8571bf84/agrupar-capas.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3127ab14-d3ca-48de-8a44-20db8571bf84/agrupar-capas.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3127ab14-d3ca-48de-8a44-20db8571bf84/agrupar-capas.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3127ab14-d3ca-48de-8a44-20db8571bf84/agrupar-capas.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3127ab14-d3ca-48de-8a44-20db8571bf84/agrupar-capas.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/3127ab14-d3ca-48de-8a44-20db8571bf84/agrupar-capas.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h3>Crear nueva capa</h3><p class="">Otro de las opciones que encontramos en el panel de capas es el de crear una nueva capa, con tan solo un clic ya tienes una nueva capa lista para trabajar.</p><p class="">También puedes crear una nueva capa, clicando en el menú superior Capa, seleccionando la opción Nueva y por último, Capa…</p><p class="">Otra forma más práctica de crear una capa es con el comando Mayús + Ctrl + N.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a1f9e72e-35c0-4c07-b986-14fb5c9cc2e5/crear-nueva-capa.jpg" data-image-dimensions="347x131" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a1f9e72e-35c0-4c07-b986-14fb5c9cc2e5/crear-nueva-capa.jpg?format=1000w" width="347" height="131" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a1f9e72e-35c0-4c07-b986-14fb5c9cc2e5/crear-nueva-capa.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a1f9e72e-35c0-4c07-b986-14fb5c9cc2e5/crear-nueva-capa.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a1f9e72e-35c0-4c07-b986-14fb5c9cc2e5/crear-nueva-capa.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a1f9e72e-35c0-4c07-b986-14fb5c9cc2e5/crear-nueva-capa.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a1f9e72e-35c0-4c07-b986-14fb5c9cc2e5/crear-nueva-capa.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a1f9e72e-35c0-4c07-b986-14fb5c9cc2e5/crear-nueva-capa.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a1f9e72e-35c0-4c07-b986-14fb5c9cc2e5/crear-nueva-capa.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h3>Eliminar capa</h3><p class="">Con esta opción podrás eliminar una o varias capas sobre las que estés trabajando. Claro, asegúrate de eliminar la capa correcta.</p>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/f6e5d288-5d18-4575-a406-4d5fc8b47359/eliminar-capa.jpg" data-image-dimensions="347x131" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/f6e5d288-5d18-4575-a406-4d5fc8b47359/eliminar-capa.jpg?format=1000w" width="347" height="131" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/f6e5d288-5d18-4575-a406-4d5fc8b47359/eliminar-capa.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/f6e5d288-5d18-4575-a406-4d5fc8b47359/eliminar-capa.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/f6e5d288-5d18-4575-a406-4d5fc8b47359/eliminar-capa.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/f6e5d288-5d18-4575-a406-4d5fc8b47359/eliminar-capa.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/f6e5d288-5d18-4575-a406-4d5fc8b47359/eliminar-capa.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/f6e5d288-5d18-4575-a406-4d5fc8b47359/eliminar-capa.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/f6e5d288-5d18-4575-a406-4d5fc8b47359/eliminar-capa.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
