        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <h2>Trípode flexible</h2>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/bb77fe5b-d36c-43b9-9d3c-05a2fd4b521f/joby-gorilla-pod.jpg" data-image-dimensions="500x405" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/bb77fe5b-d36c-43b9-9d3c-05a2fd4b521f/joby-gorilla-pod.jpg?format=1000w" width="500" height="405" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/bb77fe5b-d36c-43b9-9d3c-05a2fd4b521f/joby-gorilla-pod.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/bb77fe5b-d36c-43b9-9d3c-05a2fd4b521f/joby-gorilla-pod.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/bb77fe5b-d36c-43b9-9d3c-05a2fd4b521f/joby-gorilla-pod.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/bb77fe5b-d36c-43b9-9d3c-05a2fd4b521f/joby-gorilla-pod.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/bb77fe5b-d36c-43b9-9d3c-05a2fd4b521f/joby-gorilla-pod.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/bb77fe5b-d36c-43b9-9d3c-05a2fd4b521f/joby-gorilla-pod.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/bb77fe5b-d36c-43b9-9d3c-05a2fd4b521f/joby-gorilla-pod.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Siempre viene bien tener un trípode liviano y que se pueda cargar a cualquier lado sin mucho rollo, sin pensar en ‘‘jolines, tengo que cargar con el trípode’’</p><p class="">Una buena opción son los trípodes con patas flexibles, ya que son bastante versátiles, puedes fijarlos a postes, ramas de árboles y demás.</p><p class="">Te adelanto que uno de los mejores son los JOBY GorillaPod, así que tenlos en cuenta.</p><h2>Suscripción de Adobe Lightroom</h2>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eb8ea1ac-b817-4128-b636-b83e1ead4445/regalos-para-fotografos3.jpg" data-image-dimensions="500x333" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eb8ea1ac-b817-4128-b636-b83e1ead4445/regalos-para-fotografos3.jpg?format=1000w" width="500" height="333" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eb8ea1ac-b817-4128-b636-b83e1ead4445/regalos-para-fotografos3.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eb8ea1ac-b817-4128-b636-b83e1ead4445/regalos-para-fotografos3.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eb8ea1ac-b817-4128-b636-b83e1ead4445/regalos-para-fotografos3.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eb8ea1ac-b817-4128-b636-b83e1ead4445/regalos-para-fotografos3.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eb8ea1ac-b817-4128-b636-b83e1ead4445/regalos-para-fotografos3.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eb8ea1ac-b817-4128-b636-b83e1ead4445/regalos-para-fotografos3.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/eb8ea1ac-b817-4128-b636-b83e1ead4445/regalos-para-fotografos3.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Si tienes gran presupuesto un regalo que todo fotógrafo recibiría encantado, es una suscripción anual de Adobe Lightroom, que es el software más utilizado para la edición de fotografías.</p><h2>Estuche para tarjetas de memoria</h2>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/7fc8caf3-1140-447d-b953-fb9342b78dce/Estuche-para-tarjetas-de-memoria.jpg" data-image-dimensions="500x408" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/7fc8caf3-1140-447d-b953-fb9342b78dce/Estuche-para-tarjetas-de-memoria.jpg?format=1000w" width="500" height="408" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/7fc8caf3-1140-447d-b953-fb9342b78dce/Estuche-para-tarjetas-de-memoria.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/7fc8caf3-1140-447d-b953-fb9342b78dce/Estuche-para-tarjetas-de-memoria.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/7fc8caf3-1140-447d-b953-fb9342b78dce/Estuche-para-tarjetas-de-memoria.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/7fc8caf3-1140-447d-b953-fb9342b78dce/Estuche-para-tarjetas-de-memoria.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/7fc8caf3-1140-447d-b953-fb9342b78dce/Estuche-para-tarjetas-de-memoria.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/7fc8caf3-1140-447d-b953-fb9342b78dce/Estuche-para-tarjetas-de-memoria.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/7fc8caf3-1140-447d-b953-fb9342b78dce/Estuche-para-tarjetas-de-memoria.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">A todos los fotógrafos nos pasa que tenemos un montón de memorias, pero no tenemos donde guardarlas y muchas veces se nos pierden.</p><p class="">Así que un buen regalo para fotógrafos puede ser un estuche porta tarjetas de memorias, donde poder almacenar, ordenar y separar las que ya utilizamos y las que están disponibles para usar.</p><h2>Bolsa pequeña para cámara</h2>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                <img data-stretch="false" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a26dbe47-7399-4a13-914b-e88c8cf8b00f/bolso-peque%C3%B1o-camara.jpg" data-image-dimensions="500x293" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.5" alt="" data-load="false" elementtiming="system-image-block" src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a26dbe47-7399-4a13-914b-e88c8cf8b00f/bolso-peque%C3%B1o-camara.jpg?format=1000w" width="500" height="293" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 767px) 100vw, 100vw" onload="this.classList.add(&quot;loaded&quot;)" srcset="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a26dbe47-7399-4a13-914b-e88c8cf8b00f/bolso-peque%C3%B1o-camara.jpg?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a26dbe47-7399-4a13-914b-e88c8cf8b00f/bolso-peque%C3%B1o-camara.jpg?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a26dbe47-7399-4a13-914b-e88c8cf8b00f/bolso-peque%C3%B1o-camara.jpg?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a26dbe47-7399-4a13-914b-e88c8cf8b00f/bolso-peque%C3%B1o-camara.jpg?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a26dbe47-7399-4a13-914b-e88c8cf8b00f/bolso-peque%C3%B1o-camara.jpg?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a26dbe47-7399-4a13-914b-e88c8cf8b00f/bolso-peque%C3%B1o-camara.jpg?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d77a7f8ad30356d21445262/a26dbe47-7399-4a13-914b-e88c8cf8b00f/bolso-peque%C3%B1o-camara.jpg?format=2500w 2500w" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-loader="sqs">

            
          
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    
  


  





  <p class="">Las bolsas para cámaras suelen ser grandes y pesadas, por lo que es cansado cargar con ella todo el tiempo. Sin embargo, siempre viene bien tener la cámara protegida de los elementos.</p><p class="">Una muy buena opción es de una bolsa pequeña, donde llevar la cámara con un lente y alguna batería extra.&nbsp;</p><h2>Clip soporte para cámara</h2>





















  
  














































  

    
  
    

      

      
        <figure class="
              sqs-block-image-figure
              intrinsic
            "
        >
          
        
        

        
          
            
          
            
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
